ip - Show / manipulate routing, devices, policy routing and tunnels.

ip a
ip addr
ip link
  List interfaces.

ip link show wlan0
  Show informations from wlan0.

ip link set dev wlan0 up
  Activate a interface.

ip link set dev wlan0 down
  Deactivate a interface.

ip addr show wlan0
  Show ip address.

ip route show
  Show routes.

ip -s link
ip -stats link
  Show statistics
